Their difficulty in doing so may emanate
from difficulty in altering behavior in light of
information contrary to predictions, perhaps
in turn due to failure to form accurate predic-
tions of two sorts. First, they may have diffi-
culty adjusting to what is presented when it
violates what was expected ~or when predic-
